FORTUNE(1)             General Commands Manual            FORTUNE(1)

NAME
       fortune - sample lines from a file

SYNOPSIS
       fortune [ file ]

DESCRIPTION
       Fortune  prints  a  one-line aphorism chosen at random.  If a
       file is specified, the saying is taken from that file; other‚Äê
       wise it is selected from /lib/games/fortunes.

FILES
       /lib/games/fortunes
       /lib/games/fortunes.index    fast  lookup  table,  maintained
       automatically

SOURCE
       /appl/cmd/fortune.b

